= UK Universities

A simple web service for UK Universities data written in Ruby/Sinatra for Young Rewired State 2011.

== Examples

All Universities:
http://ukuniversities.heroku.com/universities.json
http://ukuniversities.heroku.com/universities.kml

All Russell Group Universities:
http://ukuniversities.heroku.com/universities/by/group/russell.json
http://ukuniversities.heroku.com/universities/by/group/russell.kml

All Universities costing less than Â£9000 in fees:
http://ukuniversities.heroku.com/universities/by/fees/lt/9000.json
http://ukuniversities.heroku.com/universities/by/fees/lt/9000.xml
